
To start migrations:
    Run these in terminal in proj root:
        export FLASK_APP=app       # tells Flask where your app is
        export FLASK_ENV=development  # sets development mode



=> Run Flask-Migrate commands

# Initialize migrations (only first time) # to create migrations folder
    flask db init

# Generate migration file
    flask db migrate -m "Create contact table"

# Apply migration to create tables
    flask db upgrade
